name: ERUPTION WOR(L)D
description:
The eruption of Mount Semeru is one of the unexpected natural disasters at the end of this year. Nature gives us many things, but sometimes we forget that nature also needs attention. This eruption has a very negative impact on residents around the mountain. But do you know? Nature has endured the pain caused by us, and it is time for nature to vent it. Nature will be fine without humans, but humans can do nothing without nature.

This work is part of a charity to help victims of the natural disaster from Mount Semeru eruption, every sale in the first market will be 100% donated to the victims, through sewon NFT #tezos4semeru

4000x4000 px
600 dpi
